  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.poster.avif?t=1730815137\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.webm?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.mp4?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save the throne is a simple and short game where you will fight waves of skeletons. Your goal is to protect and save the throne. Don't let them reach it or it will be game over. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some enemies are stronger, some are weaker, some are fast, some are slow. But they will all be destroyed if you shoot them enough times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you defeat a wave you will be able to choose some power ups and defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only by purchasing power ups and build stronger defenses you will be able to stand against stronger waves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.poster.avif?t=1730815137\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.webm?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.mp4?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If You Don't Know What It Is, Shoot It!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.poster.avif?t=1730815137\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.webm?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/97e8d4cac69f2c2efcf2d19215ab0389.mp4?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save the throne is a simple and short game where you will fight waves of skeletons. Your goal is to protect and save the throne. Don't let them reach it or it will be game over. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some enemies are stronger, some are weaker, some are fast, some are slow. But they will all be destroyed if you shoot them enough times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you defeat a wave you will be able to choose some power ups and defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only by purchasing power ups and build stronger defenses you will be able to stand against stronger waves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.poster.avif?t=1730815137\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.webm?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753110/extras/84d0cba1edec1601ea59c636b709de04.mp4?t=1730815137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If You Don't Know What It Is, Shoot It!</p>",
